author: Douglas Charles
title: Wait, What? Gronk Is Starring In A Real Movie With Real Actors And It Comes Out Next Month?!
text:
YouTube

Where am I? What year is this? I just found out that Rob Gronkowski, yes, GRONK , is starring in a real movie, with real actors, called You Can’t Have It and it comes out next month. Whaaaat?!
Look, there’s a movie poster with his name right there at the top and everything…

How…in the hell…did I NOT know about this?
Christ, there have even been two trailers for this flick, an IMDb page and an Instagram account this whole time…







Dafuq?

 
You Can’t Have It comes out on March 17th.
H/T Terez Owens
